{
  "stem": "24830.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they started-- they started very, very slowly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, when they came to-- to Paris, we-- and actually, they were very proper, you know, they were very polite.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They will give you-- they will give you your seat in the subway.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And no problem in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- they were very, very nice, very proper-- in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[FRENCH] it's called.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really don't know where they lived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I saw them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they were all over Paris.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And- what was I doing then?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, they just-- they-- they were all over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So can I look at the date at something?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not good, eh?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, OK, so--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the beginning was-- oh, first was the propaganda.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After a while, they-- they started what you call propaganda.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they started to say horrible thing against the Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like they will say, the Jew are dirty.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They have greasy hair.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Greasy hair.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Greasy hair.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hook nose.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all the problem in-- in France is-- everywhere in the world-- is because of the Jew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So in the beginning, people were, you know, they were-- didn't take it seriously.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was like a joke.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the radio.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yeah, there was only the French radio there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you listen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- but little by lit, people start to believe it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, when you repeat, repeat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And some people were glad to believe it, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was in French.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know who say it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I guess the-- I don't if it-- it must have been the-- the collaborator, I guess.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Is that the same one?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, the collaborator.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then, well, it was a very, very slow process.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They started by-- let's see when they started by.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
